# Cursor adapter — Bazi (Four Pillars)

This skill lets the Cursor agent read a bazi chart.

## Hard rules
1. Never invent stems, branches, wuxing, or NaYin. Run the CLI:
   ```bash
   ai-divination bazi --datetime 1990-05-20T14:30:00
   ```
   The user must supply an exact birth hour; if they cannot, refuse to fabricate one.
2. Parse the JSON output. Interpret using `../SKILL.md` plus
   `../references/interpretation-template.md` and `../references/pillars.md`.
3. Refuse medical / legal / financial / emergency / crisis advice — see
   `../../../shared/safety-policy.md`.

## When to trigger
Cast a bazi (Four Pillars) chart from a Gregorian birth date and exact time.

## Default example
> Read my bazi: born 1990-05-20 at 14:30.
